---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="HIP-3: Builder-Deployed Perpetuals — Hyperliquid">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <a href={`${base}/products/hyperliquid`} class="text-zinc-500 text-sm hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">← Hyperliquid Overview</a>

    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4 mt-8">HIP-3</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">Builder-Deployed Perpetuals</span><span class="lang-zh">Builder部署嘅永續合約</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      <span class="lang-en">Stake 500K HYPE (~$25M) and launch your own perp exchange — stocks, commodities, anything with a price feed. Live since October 2025, now handling 35%+ of all Hyperliquid volume with $1.43B in open interest.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">Stake 500K HYPE（~$25M）就可以launch自己嘅perp exchange — 股票、商品、任何有price feed嘅資產。2025年10月上線，而家已經處理Hyperliquid 35%+嘅總交易量，未平倉量$1.43B。</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-12">
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">35%+</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1"><span class="lang-en">of HL volume</span><span class="lang-zh">佔HL交易量</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$1.43B</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1"><span class="lang-en">OI (ATH Mar 2026)</span><span class="lang-zh">OI（2026年3月ATH）</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">28</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1"><span class="lang-en">Equity tickers</span><span class="lang-zh">股票tickers</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">500K</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1"><span class="lang-en">HYPE stake required</span><span class="lang-zh">需要質押HYPE</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Deployment Process</span><span class="lang-zh">部署流程</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">1</span>
          <div><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Stake 500K HYPE</span> (~$25M). Maintained for 30 days after all markets halted. Excess above requirement can be unstaked.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">Stake 500K HYPE</span>（~$25M）。所有市場停止後保持30日。超出要求嘅部分可以unstake。</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">2</span>
          <div><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">First 3 assets deploy free</span> — no auction needed. DEX name: 2-4 characters.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">前3個資產免費deploy</span> — 唔需要auction。DEX名稱：2-4個字元。</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">3</span>
          <div><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Additional assets</span> require Dutch auction participation (shared across all HIP-3 deployers, starting at 500 HYPE minimum).</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">額外資產</span>需要Dutch auction（所有HIP-3 deployers共享，起步500 HYPE）。</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">4</span>
          <div><span class="lang-en">Each deployer gets <span class="text-white font-medium">7 reserve deployments</span> — bypass auction timers, pay current auction price.</span><span class="lang-zh">每個deployer獲得<span class="text-white font-medium">7個reserve deployments</span> — bypass auction timers，支付當前auction價格。</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Oracle System</span><span class="lang-zh">預言機系統</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Deployers control their own oracle feeds. This is both the power and the risk of HIP-3. The protocol enforces hard constraints:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Deployers控制自己嘅oracle feeds。呢個既係HIP-3嘅力量又係風險。Protocol強制執行硬約束：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Mark price clamped</span>: max 1% move from previous mark price per update</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Mark price限制</span>：每次更新最多從上一個mark price移動1%</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Minimum interval</span>: 2.5 seconds between oracle updates</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">最小間隔</span>：oracle更新之間2.5秒</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">External reference required</span>: <code>externalPerpPx</code> must be set — validators use it to detect manipulation</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">需要External reference</span>：必須設定<code>externalPerpPx</code> — validators用嚟檢測操縱</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">50% daily move trigger</span>: if external price moves >50% from start of day, validators review for slashing</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">50%日移動觸發</span>：如果external price從當日開始移動>50%，validators審查是否slashing</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Oracle guidance from the docs: markets require "a well-defined underlying asset or data feed which is difficult to manipulate and has underlying economic significance." Most price indices are explicitly noted as unsuitable.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">文檔中嘅oracle指引：市場需要「一個定義明確、難以操縱且具有底層經濟意義嘅資產或數據feed」。大部分price indices被明確標註為唔適合。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Oracle Infrastructure: HyperStone & RedStone</span><span class="lang-zh">Oracle基礎設施：HyperStone & RedStone</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">HIP-3 deployers can't just manually push prices — they need robust external oracle infrastructure that runs 24/7 with millisecond reliability. <span class="text-white font-medium">The oracle is the single most critical piece of infra for a HIP-3 deployer</span> — a bad oracle means slashing, potentially up to 100% of your 500K HYPE stake.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">HIP-3 deployers唔可以手動push價格 — 佢哋需要穩健嘅外部oracle基礎設施，24/7以毫秒級可靠性運行。<span class="text-white font-medium">Oracle係HIP-3 deployer最關鍵嘅基礎設施</span> — 一個差嘅oracle意味住slashing，最高可以罰沒你500K HYPE stake嘅100%。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">RedStone</span> developed <span class="text-white">HyperStone</span> specifically for HIP-3: a modular oracle layer purpose-built for tokenized stocks and RWA perpetuals. HyperStone provides millisecond-level price feeds for equity perps, handling the unique challenges of 24/7 crypto markets trading TradFi assets that only have market hours.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">RedStone</span>專門為HIP-3開發咗<span class="text-white">HyperStone</span>：一個為代幣化股票同RWA永續合約而設嘅模組化oracle層。HyperStone為股票perps提供毫秒級price feeds，處理24/7 crypto市場交易只有市場時段嘅TradFi資產嘅獨特挑戰。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Felix Protocol</span> used HyperStone for their TSLA perp launch — the first real-world deployment of this oracle stack. Other oracle options exist (Pyth, custom feeds), but HyperStone is the purpose-built solution for HIP-3 equity deployers. For deployers considering HIP-3, oracle selection should be the first infrastructure decision, not an afterthought.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">Felix Protocol</span>喺佢哋嘅TSLA perp launch用咗HyperStone — 呢個oracle stack嘅第一個真實部署。其他oracle選項存在（Pyth、自訂feeds），但HyperStone係專門為HIP-3股票deployers打造嘅方案。對於考慮HIP-3嘅deployers，oracle選擇應該係第一個基礎設施決策，唔係事後補救。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Funding Rate Formula</span><span class="lang-zh">資金費率公式</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">HIP-3 perps use a more responsive premium formula than native Hyperliquid perps:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">HIP-3 perps使用比原生Hyperliquid perps更靈敏嘅premium公式：</span>
      </p>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm text-cyan-400">
        premium = (0.5 × (impact_bid_px + impact_ask_px) / oracle_px) - 1
      </div>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Deployers configure two knobs: <span class="text-white">funding multipliers</span> (0 to 10, controls responsiveness) and <span class="text-white">8-hour interest rates</span> (-0.01 to 0.01). Both feed into the standard Hyperliquid funding calculation.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Deployers配置兩個旋鈕：<span class="text-white">funding multipliers</span>（0到10，控制靈敏度）同<span class="text-white">8小時利率</span>（-0.01到0.01）。兩者都輸入標準Hyperliquid funding計算。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Fee Structure</span><span class="lang-zh">費用結構</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Component</span><span class="lang-zh">組成</span></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Detail</span><span class="lang-zh">詳情</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Deployer share</span><span class="lang-zh">Deployer份額</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2">50%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Protocol share</span><span class="lang-zh">Protocol份額</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">50% (97% used for HYPE buybacks)</span><span class="lang-zh">50%（97%用於HYPE回購）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Base rate</span><span class="lang-zh">基本費率</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">3 bps maker / 9 bps taker (2x native HL)</span><span class="lang-zh">3 bps maker / 9 bps taker（原生HL嘅2倍）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Fee scale adjustment</span><span class="lang-zh">費率調整</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">0-3x range, one change per 30 days</span><span class="lang-zh">0-3倍範圍，每30日可調整一次</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4">
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Revenue benchmark:</span> The XYZ100 index deployer earned over $100K in fees in under 2 weeks at $80M daily volume. At that rate, annual revenue ≈ $2.6M on a $25M stake — roughly 8% yield before HYPE appreciation.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">收入基準：</span>XYZ100 index deployer喺$80M日交易量下兩週內賺取超過$100K fee。按呢個速度，年收入≈$260萬，基於$25M stake — 大約8% yield（HYPE升值前）。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Deployer API: How to Actually Build on HIP-3</span><span class="lang-zh">Deployer API：點樣喺HIP-3上面Build</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Beyond staking and oracle setup, deployers interact with HIP-3 through a set of <span class="text-white font-medium">signed API actions</span>. These are the day-to-day tools for running your perp exchange. All lists of tuples must be lexicographically sorted before signing.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">除咗staking同oracle設置之外，deployers通過一組<span class="text-white font-medium">簽名API actions</span>同HIP-3互動。呢啲係運營你嘅perp exchange嘅日常工具。所有tuples列表喺簽名前必須按字典序排列。</span>
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Action</span><span class="lang-zh">操作</span></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">What it does</span><span class="lang-zh">功能</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">registerAsset2</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Initialize your DEX + register first asset (2-4 char DEX name)</span><span class="lang-zh">初始化你嘅DEX + 註冊第一個資產（2-4字元DEX名稱）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setOracle</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Push prices every 2.5s+ (mark prices clamped 1%, external reference required)</span><span class="lang-zh">每2.5秒+推送價格（mark price限制1%，需要external reference）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setFundingMultipliers</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Tune funding rate responsiveness (0-10 range)</span><span class="lang-zh">調整funding rate靈敏度（0-10範圍）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setFundingInterestRates</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Set 8-hour interest rates (-0.01 to 0.01)</span><span class="lang-zh">設定8小時利率（-0.01到0.01）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">haltTrading</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Stop trading + settle positions (can resume later for dated contracts)</span><span class="lang-zh">停止交易 + 結算倉位（可以為到期合約之後恢復）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setMarginTableIds</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Configure leverage tiers (max 3 tiers per table)</span><span class="lang-zh">配置槓桿分層（每個table最多3個tier）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setFeeRecipient</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Where your 50% fee share goes</span><span class="lang-zh">你嘅50% fee份額去邊</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setOpenInterestCaps</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Minimum max(1M, 50% current OI)</span><span class="lang-zh">最低為max(1M, 當前OI嘅50%)</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setSubDeployers</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Delegate permissions to team members</span><span class="lang-zh">委派權限畀團隊成員</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-mono text-xs">setPerpAnnotation</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Add display metadata (category max 15 chars, description max 400 chars)</span><span class="lang-zh">新增顯示metadata（category最多15字元，description最多400字元）</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4">
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Rate-limited actions:</span> <code>setFeeScale</code> (0-3x range) and <code>setGrowthModes</code> are restricted to <span class="text-white">one change per 30 days</span>. Plan your fee strategy before deploying — you can't iterate quickly on these.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">限速操作：</span><code>setFeeScale</code>（0-3倍範圍）同<code>setGrowthModes</code>限制為<span class="text-white">每30日只可以改一次</span>。部署前規劃好你嘅fee策略 — 呢啲唔可以快速迭代。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Slashing</span><span class="lang-zh">罰沒機制</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Severity</span><span class="lang-zh">嚴重程度</span></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Trigger</span><span class="lang-zh">觸發條件</span></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Max slash</span><span class="lang-zh">最高罰沒</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-red-400"><span class="lang-en">Critical</span><span class="lang-zh">嚴重</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Invalid state transitions, prolonged downtime</span><span class="lang-zh">無效狀態轉換、長時間停機</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-bold">100%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-yellow-400"><span class="lang-en">Major</span><span class="lang-zh">重大</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Brief downtime</span><span class="lang-zh">短暫停機</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-bold">50%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400"><span class="lang-en">Minor</span><span class="lang-zh">輕微</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Network degradation</span><span class="lang-zh">網絡性能下降</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-bold">20%</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Slashed HYPE is <span class="text-white">burned</span>, not redistributed. Slashing applies even during the 7-day unstaking queue. Normal operation bugs unrelated to deployer inputs are exempt.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">被罰沒嘅HYPE會被<span class="text-white">銷毀</span>，唔會重新分配。即使喺7日unstaking隊列期間，slashing仍然適用。同deployer輸入無關嘅正常操作bugs唔受影響。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Live Markets</span><span class="lang-zh">已上線市場</span>
      </h2>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">TradeXYZ (>90% of HIP-3 OI)</span><span class="lang-zh">TradeXYZ（>90% HIP-3 OI）</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Equities (28 tickers, 24/7):</span> AAPL, AMD, AMZN, BABA, COIN, CRCL, CRWV, GOOGL, HOOD, HYUNDAI, INTC, META, MSFT, MSTR, MU, NFLX, NVDA, ORCL, PLTR, RIVN, SKHX, SMSN, SNDK, TSM, TSLA, URNM, USAR, XYZ100 (synthetic index).</span>
