        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Felix Protocol</span> — 用HyperStone/RedStone oracle層launch TSLA perp。<span class="text-white">Ventuals</span> — launch SPACEX perp。<span class="text-white">S&P Dow Jones Indices</span> — 正式授權品牌用於第一個鏈上S&P 500永續合約。</span>
