      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Important Limitations</span><span class="lang-zh">重要限制</span>
      </h2>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Isolated margin only</span> — cross-margin planned but not yet available. Enabling cross-margin on an asset is irreversible.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">只有Isolated margin</span> — cross-margin計劃中但尚未推出。資產嘅cross-margin啟用係不可逆嘅。</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">No HLP backstop</span> — Hyperliquid's own liquidity pool does NOT market-make HIP-3 markets. Deployers must attract their own MMs.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">冇HLP支持</span> — Hyperliquid自己嘅liquidity pool唔會為HIP-3市場做市。Deployers必須自己吸引MMs。</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Deployer trust</span> — you trust the deployer's oracle, margin settings, and operational competence, not just Hyperliquid core.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Deployer信任</span> — 你信嘅係deployer嘅oracle、margin設定同運營能力，唔單止Hyperliquid core。</span></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Settlement & Market Recycling</span><span class="lang-zh">結算同市場回收</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The <code>haltTrading</code> action isn't just an emergency stop — it's a <span class="text-white font-medium">full lifecycle tool</span>. When a market is halted, all open orders are cancelled and positions settle to current mark price.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><code>haltTrading</code>唔只係緊急停止 — 佢係一個<span class="text-white font-medium">完整嘅生命週期工具</span>。當市場被暫停時，所有open orders被取消，倉位以當前mark price結算。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Critical detail:</span> halted markets <span class="text-white">CAN be resumed</span> — the asset gets recycled. This enables dated/expiring contracts without needing to pay new auction fees each time. A deployer can run weekly oil futures — halt Friday, settle all positions, resume Monday with a fresh orderbook.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">關鍵細節：</span>暫停嘅市場<span class="text-white">可以恢復</span> — 資產會被回收。呢個功能令到期合約唔使每次都支付新嘅auction費用。Deployer可以run每週嘅石油期貨 — 星期五暫停，結算所有倉位，星期一用全新orderbook恢復。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Once <span class="text-white">ALL</span> assets on a deployer's DEX are halted and settled, the deployer's stake becomes eligible for unstaking (subject to the 30-day hold period). This is the only way to exit — you can't unstake while any market is still live.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">一旦deployer嘅DEX上<span class="text-white">所有</span>資產都暫停同結算咗，deployer嘅stake就符合unstaking資格（受30日持有期限制）。呢個係唯一嘅退出方式 — 任何市場仲live緊都唔可以unstake。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Cross-Margin: The Path Forward</span><span class="lang-zh">Cross-Margin：前路</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Currently HIP-3 markets are <span class="text-white">isolated margin only</span> — cross-margin is the most requested feature. Why it matters: cross-margin dramatically improves capital efficiency for traders, letting them use one collateral pool for all HIP-3 positions instead of locking up separate margin per market.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">目前HIP-3市場只有<span class="text-white">isolated margin</span> — cross-margin係最多人要求嘅功能。點解重要：cross-margin大幅提升trader嘅資本效率，令佢哋可以用一個collateral pool覆蓋所有HIP-3倉位，唔使每個市場鎖定獨立margin。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Enabling cross-margin on an asset is IRREVERSIBLE</span> — can't go back to isolated. Validators enforce strict eligibility criteria: sufficient observable liquidity, reliable external oracle, and manipulation resistance. There's also a monthly frequency check: if an asset has >50% daily moves more than once per month, it's ineligible for cross-margin.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">資產啟用cross-margin係不可逆嘅</span> — 唔可以返返去isolated。Validators強制執行嚴格嘅資格標準：足夠嘅可觀察流動性、可靠嘅external oracle、同抗操縱能力。仲有月度頻率檢查：如果一個資產每月超過一次出現>50%日波動，就唔符合cross-margin資格。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">TradeXYZ</span> recently enabled cross-margin across silver, gold, and S&P 500 — the first deployer to achieve this milestone. This signals growing confidence from validators in HIP-3 market quality and sets the template for other deployers to follow.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">TradeXYZ</span>最近喺白銀、黃金同S&P 500上啟用咗cross-margin — 第一個達到呢個里程碑嘅deployer。呢個信號表明validators對HIP-3市場質量嘅信心增長，亦為其他deployers樹立咗模板。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">EaaS: Lowering the $25M Barrier</span><span class="lang-zh">EaaS：降低$25M門檻</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The 500K HYPE staking requirement (~$25M) limits who can deploy. But a new category of <span class="text-white font-medium">Exchange-as-a-Service (EaaS)</span> solutions is emerging. Protocols like Kinetiq Research's Launch enable delegated staking and risk tranching — smaller builders can crowdfund the capital requirement through pools, effectively democratizing market deployment. This transforms HYPE from a governance token into <span class="text-white">infrastructure capital</span>: holders earn yield by contributing to protocol infrastructure, not just voting.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">500K HYPE staking要求（~$25M）限制咗邊個可以deploy。但一個新嘅<span class="text-white font-medium">Exchange-as-a-Service（EaaS）</span>類別正在出現。Kinetiq Research嘅Launch等protocol允許delegated staking同risk tranching — 小型builder可以通過pooling眾籌資本要求，有效地democratize市場部署。呢個將HYPE從governance token轉變為<span class="text-white">infrastructure capital</span>：持有者通過貢獻protocol基礎設施嚟賺取yield，唔只係投票。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Revenue Diversification: From Crypto to TradFi</span><span class="lang-zh">收入多元化：從Crypto到TradFi</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">HIP-3's most important economic impact is shifting Hyperliquid's revenue base from crypto market volatility to the <span class="text-white font-medium">stable, massive trading volumes of traditional financial markets</span> (equities, commodities, FX). Arete Capital estimates annualized protocol revenue at $1.13B (Q3 2025), projected to reach $1.87B by end of 2026 (+65%). Key growth drivers: HyperCore (+$415M), Builder Codes (+$154M), Aligned Stablecoins (+$88M), HIP-3 markets (+$80M). This diversification transforms HYPE's value proposition from speculative to infrastructure-usage-based.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">HIP-3最重要嘅經濟影響係將Hyperliquid嘅收入基礎從crypto市場波動性轉移到<span class="text-white font-medium">傳統金融市場嘅穩定巨量</span>（股票、商品、FX）。Arete Capital估算年化protocol收入$11.3億（2025年Q3），預計2026年底達$18.7億（+65%）。主要增長驅動：HyperCore（+$4.15億）、Builder Codes（+$1.54億）、Aligned Stablecoins（+$0.88億）、HIP-3市場（+$0.8億）。呢個多元化將HYPE嘅價值主張從投機性轉變為基於infrastructure使用嘅模式。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Why dYdX Failed Where Hyperliquid Succeeded</span><span class="lang-zh">點解dYdX失敗而Hyperliquid成功</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">dYdX launched permissionless perps in 2024. Their Tesla xStock does $4K daily volume. Hyperliquid's TSLA does $26M+. The difference isn't technology — it's distribution. Hyperliquid has tens of thousands of daily active users, $200M+ daily spot volume, and MetaMask integration reaching 30M wallets. You can build the best perp infra in the world, but without users already on the platform, no one trades your new markets.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">dYdX喺2024年推出permissionless perps。佢哋嘅Tesla xStock日交易量$4K。Hyperliquid嘅TSLA係$26M+。差別唔係技術 — 係distribution。Hyperliquid有數萬日活用戶、$200M+日現貨交易量、同MetaMask整合覆蓋30M錢包。你可以build世界上最好嘅perp infra，但如果platform上冇用戶，冇人會交易你嘅新市場。</span>
      </p>

